### Create a Checklist
POST http://localhost:8080/api/todolist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Belanja Bulanan"
}

### Get All Checklists
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todolist
Accept: application/json

### Get a Checklist by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todolist/1
Accept: application/json

### Add Item to a Checklist
POST http://localhost:8080/api/todolist/1/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Beli Beras",
  "completed": false
}

### Add Item to a Checklist
PATCH  http://localhost:8080/api/todolist/items/1/status?completed=true
Content-Type: application/json
